cies, attributed to SNe. The broader issue of Galactic\nChemical Evolution is also discussed in view of the isotopic granularity in the\nISM. \\end{abstract}\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 8 Mar 2015 08:31:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-27"}
