 devise such\nlocal Hamiltonians that resist approximation in terms of bounded-depth quantum\ncircuits (e.g. NLTS), and even find such robust forms of entanglement that are\nuseful for some computation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 8 Mar 2015 12:12:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 Apr 2015 17:30:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 4 Jun 2015 00:55:55 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 23 Feb 2017 19:20:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-27"}
